{"tid":694673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★工作問題困擾 90後跳樓亡","createTime":"2018-06-08T14:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T14:22:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6710f38225dcaf125c391462a30570f42e714f13","tid":694673,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"沙田沙角邨發生男子墮樓死亡案。一名姓葉(24歲)男子，傍晚6時許，在銀鷗樓高處墮下，現場因有外牆進行維修，地上置有一個吊船，男事主跌落吊船旁邊，重傷血泊昏迷，葉父(56歲)發現報警，救護員接報到場，將傷者送院搶救，惜證實不治。據悉，死者生前居住現場大廈一單位，任職店務員，疑<span style=\"color: red;\">近日受工作問題困擾</span>，事發前接聽一通電話後，突然情緒激動，走出走廊一躍而下，警方將進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180608/bkn-20180608204832296-0608_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180608%2Fbkn-20180608204832296-0608_00822_001.html&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0dff5243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180608/bkn-20180608204832296-0608_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8458ccb99ec4967e314b3847a7f7d97e60b676b9","tid":694673,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9b3d4fcd671f6636106c6ff34831705443db441","tid":694673,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"公屋，做低下工作<br />\n投胎好過"},{"pid":"c9b497ee1a45a3bc3bd03b41e68ecfbf15970e7c","tid":694673,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44fc3e613839c3a0402a046395bea96585a31c69","tid":694673,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回